*Stanicu* je čekao na platformi pola sata. (He was waiting at the station for half an hour.)

Na *stanici* su se čule vesele pesme. (Happy songs were heard at the station.)

Zadnji put je stigao u *stanicu* u tri sata popodne. (He arrived at the station for the last time at three in the afternoon.)

Malo dete je tražilo svoju majku na *stanici*. (A little child was looking for his mother at the station.)

*Stanica* je bila puna ljudi. (The station was full of people.)